Package com.mpagliaro98.mysubscriptions.ui.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CalendarEventHandler
    Interface to implement for classes that act as an event handler for the subscription calendar.
    OnDataListenerReceived
    Fragments that implement this interface will be a receiver of new Subscription objects.
    OnSyncCalendarListener
    Fragments that implement this interface can become sync calendar listeners for MainActivity.
    SavedStateCompatible
    An interface to denote pages that are compatible with saved state bundles.
